sequenceDiagram
    participant Hardware as USB Serial (SiK Radio)
    participant Node as Node.js IPC Thread
    participant Chromium as Chromium Main Thread
    participant Zustand as React / Zustand Store
    
    Note over Hardware,Node: Ingress Speed: 57,600 bps
    
    loop Every ~100ms (10Hz)
        Hardware->>Node: Raw Uint8Array Chunk
        activate Node
        Node->>Node: Parse Magic Bytes (0xFD)\nVerify CRC-X25 Checksum
        Node->>Node: Decode MAVLink Payload to JSON
        Node-->>Chromium: IPC Send: 'telemetry_update' (Latency: < 0.5ms)
        deactivate Node
        
        activate Chromium
        Chromium->>Zustand: store.updateState(JSON)
        activate Zustand
        Zustand-->>Chromium: Diffing State Selectors (Latency: < 1.0ms)
        deactivate Zustand
        Chromium->>Chromium: Render Cycle (60 FPS)\nUpdate SVG transforms
        deactivate Chromium
    end
